This map was created originally by Cleav420

This is #11 map i have made.

Well this is a storage area map.

You will see that there are alot of doors to storage units
and some spawn in them.

There is also an area with buliding work with a crain you can
get on.

And there are rooms as well to hide in.
Cargo area in the map where you can jump on fence to run
to storage area.

So enjoy the map and please leave comment about map.

Also if any one likes the few maps i made you can x-fire me @ cleav420
Or visit my ventrilo for info on how to better my maps,

Or even work with me together on one of my maps.
Thx .:{Cleav420}:.
